                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220911-219-off1168 t18220911-219-cd1169"></join>, two shirts, value 10 s.; three pair of stockings, value 5 s.; and one shift, value 2 s., and one towel, value 6 d.
